Description: GNU Datamash is a command-line program which performs basicnumeric,textual and statistical operations on input textual data files.It is designed to be portable and reliable, and aid researchersto easily automate analysis pipelines, without writing code or even short scripts.License: GPL Version 3 (or later).These tool wrappers were originally writen by Assaf Gordon.
